## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9d17d-122">Un lessico pronuncia è una raccolta di parole o frasi con le pronunce specificate mediante un alfabeto pronuncia appropriato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d17d-122">A pronunciation lexicon is a collection of words or phrases together with their pronunciations specified using an appropriate pronunciation alphabet.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9d17d-123">Questo metodo viene in genere chiamato dall'infrastruttura della piattaforma in risposta a un <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis> basato su applicazioni che chiamano <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A> e l'uso della voce di sintetizzatore implementata dall'oggetto corrente <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml> istanza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d17d-123">This method is typically called by the platform infrastructure in response to a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis> based applications calling <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A> and using the synthesizer voice implemented by the current <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml> instance.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9d17d-124">Il valore di `mediaType` è in genere una specifica MIME, la specifica SSML utilizza MIME per le specifiche dei supporti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d17d-124">The value of `mediaType` is typically a MIME specification, as the SSML specification uses MIME for media specifications.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="9d17d-125">L'implementazione di <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A> utilizza il <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> interfaccia passato per caricare un lessico da una risorsa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d17d-125">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A> uses the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> interface passed in to load a lexicon from a resource.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9d17d-126">Archivia un `System.IO.Stream` per il dizionario in una `System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary` istanza, indicizzato da lessico URI.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d17d-126">It then stores a `System.IO.Stream` to the lexicon in a `System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary` instance, indexed by the lexicon URI.</span></span>  
  
```  
public static Dictionary<Uri, Stream> _aLexicons = new Dictionary<Uri, Stream>();  
  
 public void AddLexicon(Uri uri, string mediaType, ITtsEngineSite site) {  
    Stream stream = site.LoadResource(uri, mediaType);  
    _aLexicons.Add(uri, stream);  
}  
  
 public void RemoveLexicon(Uri uri, ITtsEngineSite site) {  
     Stream stream;  
     if (_aLexicons.TryGetValue(uri, out stream)) {  
         stream.Close();  
         _aLexicons.Remove(uri);  
     }  
}  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9d17d-133">La struttura utilizzata come `targetWaveFormat` e restituito dal metodo deve compatibile con il `WAVEFORMATEX` disponibile nel SAPI, e il valore restituito deve essere allocato tramite `CoTaskMemAlloc`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d17d-133">The structure used as `targetWaveFormat` and returned by the method should compatible with the `WAVEFORMATEX` available under SAPI, and the returned value should be allocated using `CoTaskMemAlloc`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9d17d-134">Il `struct` deve fornire funzionalità equivalente a:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9d17d-134">The `struct` must provide functionality equivalent to:</span></span>  
  
```  
internal struct WaveFormat  
{  
    public Int16 FormatTag;  
    public Int16 Channels;  
    public int SamplesPerSec;  
    public int AvgBytesPerSec;  
